    Scope and Contents
Only the data summaries (Boxes 1 &amp; 2) are open to inspection. Access to tapes and transcripts are RESTRICTED and requires written permission from the CSMC.  
This records group consists of recorded interviews with Asian-Americans about their lives in and their feelings about America and Springfield Illinois.  Subjects from various countries, including Pakistan, Korea, China, Philippines and India.  
  
    Arrangement Note
Project records, then oral history interviews alphabetically by name of person  
  
    Conditions Governing Access
Partially RESTRICTED.  
The oral history tapes and transcripts are restricted indefinietely as respondents were promised confidentiality.  Access can only be with permission from the Center.  
  
